title: Yahoo Lifestyle
text: Waves of impatience come and go today, prompting your emotions to vary widely as you bounce around from topic to topic. In fact, people may have a difficult time anticipating and discerning your moods and leanings. However, you could be just as irritated as everyone else since you cant seem to make up your mind now. Fortunately, you can choose to lead with your heart by focusing less attention on your needs and more on acts of service. Educator Booker T. Washington wrote, Those who are happiest are those who do the most for others. Get Your Complete Cosmic Profile
